	<header class="entry-header">
		
		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2005/02/new-york-meetings-touring/" rel="bookmark">New York Meetings: Touring New York</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	
	
	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>My first Valentines day with Alex, and I have to be 3,500 kilometres from her.<br />
It could be worse. I could be in Kanata.<br />
 <a href="http://geoff.wp/2005/02/new-york-meetings-touring/#more-457" class="more-link">Continue reading<span class="screen-reader-text"> &#8220;New York Meetings: Touring New York&#8221;</span></a></p>
	</div><!-- .entry-content -->

